QuestData.Title: Beyond Durotar
QuestData.Description: Hmmph... it looks like your services are being requested elsewhere. Ag'tor Bloodfist is looking for recruits to assist the Horde's ventures in Azshara, north of Orgrimmar.$b$bI'm sure you still have work to do here in Durotar, and I understand that they'll shortly be asking for your help in the Barrens. I wouldn't be going anywhere yet if I were you, but if you're itching for some manifest destiny... Azshara awaits.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Ag'tor Bloodfist at the Orgrimmar Rear Gate in Azshara.
QuestData.RewardText: Good, you're here. Welcome to Azshara, the stage for the next act of the Horde's glorious future. Now get to work.
